{"tid":1523424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"罷搭狗鐵唔撚該！！！","createTime":"2019-08-31T15:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T16:07:34.000Z","uid":202272,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5dc59c4691207e37e734976e1f1d95049fbcc4de","tid":1523424,"uid":202272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:46:21.000Z","msg":"我係垃圾和理非亦冇勇氣走去前線同班狗去對抗<br />\n但大家可唔可以去做一啲實際行動去支持勇武 我哋已經冇上前線仲要受前線保護 點解唔去做多幾步去表示支持 <br />\n<br />\n我明狗鐵係最快最方便嘅交通 <br />\n但麻煩大家睇清楚 啱啱狗鐵點樣對我哋嘅手足 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係又直接封站</span> 令到一車嘅手足俾班狗困獸鬥啊 咁同721有乜撚野分別 一見黑衫就追住嚟打  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">根本狗鐵就睇死我哋香港人冇得唔搭狗鐵 冇撚咗佢香港人會唔撚掂 所以就不斷去挑戰我地底線 關站放狗<br />\n當你繼續去搭狗鐵就等同於助紂為虐</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當我求下大家 翻工嘅可唔可以早小小起身 搭巴士又好小巴都好 唔好再為方便而搭狗鐵令佢哋有恃無恐 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷狗鐵！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我依家開始就算搭狗鐵我都會跳閘 一蚊都唔撚俾佢"},{"pid":"6473177991d4d2b013a81359007aacba0c923e0a","tid":1523424,"uid":84614,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:49:32.000Z","msg":"直接拆撚左狗鐵站去"},{"pid":"58d24ba8281770298726e4343c97df428c80ba11","tid":1523424,"uid":202272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:53:22.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 真係好撚嬲"},{"pid":"267e76bf6a8c0dced5b86a7acfd4bdd640ce0db8","tid":1523424,"uid":202272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:53:57.000Z","msg":"我以後行路都路唔撚會搭啊 仆你個臭街"},{"pid":"03a94447138134eebd33dedee6c36f35237529ef","tid":1523424,"uid":90883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:54:43.000Z","msg":"我會積極開始罷搭"},{"pid":"59cba98071dbc358247d69db70956d5558cccdc7","tid":1523424,"uid":202272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:56:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷狗鐵啊大家 香港人唔好再咁善忘啊 諗下今晚俾狗鐵封站有幾多手足俾班狗捉咗翻去狗屋撚 </span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"217fa65bcac522a791f5beae973ca47fce7c34eb","tid":1523424,"uid":216080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:57:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55789ec493cfe227b64209030649f65af14c9ccf","tid":1523424,"uid":233443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:58:11.000Z","msg":"罷搭呀 dklm!!"},{"pid":"186082c27d8b74a45c7269887fb030a6e4e6797a","tid":1523424,"uid":202272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:01:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">聽日機場見</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n搭嘅話記得跳閘啊 咪撚好似今日咁個個喺度排隊等買飛<br />\n俾啲勇氣 我今日都喺第一次試跳 真喺好撚易 <br />\n<br />\n我仲要1米7都冇啊 唔該大家俾啲信心自己 咪撚俾錢狗鐵"},{"pid":"b786aaec962ef6d94e233a967baa0ec28895391a","tid":1523424,"uid":202272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:06:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"358ab1a274cd0a0b3c6516d4ba095f22136ce1d4","tid":1523424,"uid":202272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:06:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c75fd62f883aa63b9bb63ad4f4d83cc98c8e289","tid":1523424,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:07:29.000Z","msg":"#HongKongProtest<br />\n#hkpolicebrutality<br />\n#antielab<br />\n#terroristhkpolice<br />\n#terroristhkpolice<br />\n#whatishappeninginhk<br />\n#whatishappeninginhongkong<br />\n#whathappeninhongkong<br />\n#hkpoliceforce<br />\n#831hkpolice<br />\n#prayforhk"},{"pid":"a734083eba9370c8bd2c905a82ebf528e5063d7e","tid":1523424,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:07:34.000Z","msg":"罰抄一百次以後不搭黨鐵<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1523674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1523674</a><br />\n<br />\n係直頭唔搭<br />\n依加影響到乘客安全<br />\n同洗唔洗錢已經無關"}]}